Copy rquired files to corresponding folder

if need to update 

DRIVER copy new driver to the /update_files/driver folder
APPLIATION copy new application to the /update_files/application folder
SCRIPTS copy new driver to the /update_files/scripts folder
SERVER copy new driver to the /update_files/server folder


compress dcu_update folder in tar.gz format

upload new file using maintanance in the local server

(WARNING!!! updating driver and app_checking_deamon.sh ethernet_checking.sh will reboot the system )
